提出抗告狀。\r\n                                      書記官  邱紹銓\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　12　　月　　24　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPHM/110%2c%e8%81%b2%2c4488%2c20211224%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,110,聲,4488,20211224,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"4488","JDATE":"20211224","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}